          "content": "### MAJOR ANDERSON IS DOWN\n\n**TIME:** 12:00 PM EST, October 27\n\nThis is the darkest moment of the crisis. Word reaches the White House that a U-2 spy plane, piloted by Major Rudolf Anderson, has disappeared from radar over Banes, Cuba. \n\n**The Confirmation:**\nIntercepted communications confirm the plane was destroyed by a Soviet SA-2 'Guideline' surface-to-air missile (SAM). Major Anderson is dead. He is the first combat casualty of the Cuban Missile Crisis.\n\n**The Standing Orders:**\nThe Pentagon is in an uproar. Prior to this, the ExComm had agreed on 'Standing Orders': If a US reconnaissance plane was fired upon, the US would *immediately* retaliate by destroying the SAM site responsible. If the plane was shot down, the US would destroy *all* SAM sites in Cuba. The Air Force jets in Florida are fueled, armed, and waiting for the Presidential 'Go' code."
